  "text": "Strict standardized conditions were applied during testing to minimize confounders [CITATION_1] . All stroke patients were enrolled within the first 3 days, and tests were completed within 5 days of stroke onset, to lower the effect of difference in vascular instability during the acute phase poststroke.",
